org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns.merge

Interface GeneralColumnTitleChooser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AverageNumber, FirstQuartileNumber, InterQuartileRangeNumber, JoinNumberColumns, MaximumNumber, MedianNumber, SumNumbers

    public interface GeneralColumnTitleChooser
    Interface that general merge strategies that only need to choose a title for the column to create should implement in order to be able to use GeneralColumnTitleChooserUI.
    Author:
    Eduardo Ramos
